Steps to Make your own Login Authentication

# your system must have node js --> this requires a older version (20)
# and u may need to install that and then type a command
---> nvm use 20 
Also u should be having a mongodb compass for handling databases!
Install requirements
command below >>
---> npm install express  ( Express.js - For handling routes )
      It will install
     --> required node modules
     --> package json files
     --> package lock json files
---> npm install mongoose  ( MongoDB & Mongoose - For storing user data )
---> npm install bcrypt  ( bcrypt - For password encryption )
---> npm install ejs ( EJS - For rendering dynamic pages )
